.DT
colour_event
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
colour_event

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
colour_event -  This function returns the appropriate colour codes for the given event type.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string colour_event(string event_type,
string default_colour)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^event_type%^RESET%^ - The type of event
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
a string of colour codes.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/events.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function returns the appropriate colour codes for the given event
type. It will return the players chosen colour if they've set one or
the default if not.

.EP

